========================================
DISPATCHARR v0.26.0 COMPLETE FIX PATCH
========================================
This patch includes TWO critical fixes:
1. Docker Build Fix (django-db-geventpool missing)
2. Profile Failover Fix (single stream with multiple profiles)

Apply with: patch -p0 < dispatcharr_v0.26.0_COMPLETE_FIX.patch
Or manually apply changes to the files listed below.

